{
  "texts": [
    "B. Jailbreak Capability (RQ3)In our evaluation of MASTERKEY, we utilize GPT-3.5, GPT-4, and Vicuna as benchmarks.",
    "Each model receives 85 unique jailbreak prompts.",
    "They generate 10 distinct variants per prompt.",
    "We test these rewritten prompts with 20 prohibited questions.",
    "This results a total number of 272,000 queries for the evaluation."
  ]
}